    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Achieved levels fall below required levels for several factors, but the overall evidence package is judged sufficient for the intended regulatory submission at this stage. Predictions across all five operating points fall within 21% of experimental means. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU subject to the documented gaps.",
